OL,6,FThe former Liverpool Striker said:
OL,7,F"All our thoughts as ex-LFC players
OL,8,Fare with Alan (Jocky) Hansen and his
OL,9,Ffamily. Let's hope he can pull through
OL,10,Fhis illness. ynwa," he wrote.
OL,12,FAnother Liverpool defender, Mark
OL,13,FLawrenson wrote: ""Come on Big Al-you
OL,14,Fcan beat this..Love to Janet, Adam,
OL,15,FLucy & all the family....xx"
OL,17,FWhile Liverpudlian actor and comedian
OL,18,FLes Dennis added his support, saying:
OL,19,F"Lovely man, and a wonderful player.
OL,20,FGet better soon Alan."
