OL,6,FHansen, also known as "Jocky", began
OL,7,Fhis successful career as a television
OL,8,Fpundit in 1992 until 2014.
OL,10,FHis former Match of the Day colleague
OL,11,FGary Lineker wrote on X: "Horrendous
OL,12,Fnews. Thoughts are with Alan, Janet
OL,13,Fand all the family."
OL,15,FEverton FC also sent a message of
OL,16,Fsupport to the football legend on X
OL,17,Fwhich read: "Get well soon, Alan. Our
OL,18,Fthoughts and prayers are with you and
OL,19,Fyour loved ones."
