OL,6,FThe BBC's Match of the Day X account
OL,7,Fsaid: "The thoughts and prayers of
OL,8,Feveryone at Match of the Day are with
OL,9,FAlan and his family at this difficult
OL,10,Ftime."
OL,12,FHansen joined Liverpool from Partick
OL,13,FThistle in 1977 and won three European
OL,14,FCups, eight league titles, two FA Cups
OL,15,Fand three League Cups in 620
OL,16,Fappearances for the Anfield side.
OL,18,FHe also won 26 caps for Scotland
OL,19,Fbetween 1979 and 1987 and played in
OL,20,Fthe 1982 World Cup.
