OL,6,FFollowing the news, current assistant
OL,7,Fmanager of the national side, John
OL,8,FCarver, sent a message of support from
OL,9,Fthe Euro 2024 camp wishing Hansen well.
OL,11,FHe said: "I would just like to pass a
OL,12,Fmessage on to say that everybody, the
OL,13,Fplayers, the staff, everybody
OL,14,Fconnected with the SFA, are really
OL,15,Fthinking about himself and his family
OL,16,Fbecause it is an extremely difficult
OL,17,Ftime.
OL,19,F"The biggest thing that I noticed was
OL,20,Fthat he was a fantastic defender but
OL,21,Fhe was a ball playing centre-half.
